Compound of {{m|ja||踏み|tr=fumi}}, the {{m|ja|連用形|tr=ren'yōkei||stem or continuative form}} of verb {{m|ja|踏む|tr=fumu||to [[step]], [[tread]]}} + {{m|ja||絆|tr=hodashi|[[rope]] to [[bind]] an [[horse]], for example, as not to [[get away]]}}.
